> fixing:
>
> 1. **Rotate** the exposed secret immediately — assume it's burned.
> 2. **Audit** how it reached the session (`cat .env`? pasted inline?
>    echoed by a tool?) and close that path.
> 3. **Substitute** placeholder values in prompts and let the session look
>    up the real thing at run time from an env var or secret store you
>    don't read through Claude.

